    </teiHeader>
    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="transcript" id="J944">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>I learned -- at least -- what Home could be --</l>
                    <l>How ignorant I had been</l>
                    <l>Of pretty ways of Covenant --</l>
                    <l>How awkward at <app type="revision"><lem>the Plan</lem><rdg>the Plan</rdg></app>
the Hymn</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Round our new Fireside -- but for this --</l>
                    <l>This pattern -- of the Way --</l>
                    <l>Whose Memory drowns me, like the Dip</l>
                    <l>Of a Celestial Sea --</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>What Mornings in our Garden -- guessed --</l>
                    <l>What Bees -- for us -- to hum --</l>
                    <l>With only <app type="revision"><lem>Bloom</lem><rdg>Bloom</rdg></app>
Birds to interrupt</l>
                    <l>The Ripple of our Theme --</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>And Task for Both --</l>
                    <l>When Play be done --</l>
                    <l>Your <app type="revision"><lem>labor</lem><rdg>labor</rdg></app>
Problem -- of the Brain --</l>
                    <l>And mine -- some foolisher effect --</l>
                    <l>A <app type="revision"><lem>Thimble</lem><rdg>Thimble</rdg></app>
Ruffle -- or a Tune --</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>The Afternoons -- Together spent --</l>
                    <l>And Twilight -- in the Lanes --</l>
                    <l>Some ministry to poorer lives --</l>
                    <l>Seen poorest -- thro' our gains --</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>And then Return -- and <app type="revision"><lem>Trust</lem><rdg>Trust</rdg></app>
Night -- and Home --</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>And then away to You to pass --</l>
                    <l>A new -- diviner -- care --</l>
                    <l>Till Sunrise <app type="revision"><lem>call --</lem><rdg>call --</rdg></app>
take us back to Scene --</l>
                    <l>Transmuted -- Vivider --</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>This seems a Home --</l>
                    <l>And Home is not --</l>
                    <l>But what that Place could be --</l>
                    <l>Afflicts me -- as a Setting Sun --</l>
                    <l>Where Dawn -- knows how to be --</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                </lg>

            </div>     
